Package: cm108d
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libusb-1.0-0
Description: Pure-Rust real-time audio server for CM108/CM119 USB devices
 cm108d replaces the ALSA snd-usb-audio driver for C-Media CM108/CM119
 USB audio chips used in amateur radio repeater systems. It provides
 deterministic sub-5ms audio I/O and direct HID GPIO access for PTT/COS
 control via SCHED_FIFO real-time threads.
